				<h2 class="text-xl opacity-80 text-wrap-pretty">Front-End Developer Exploring Back-End Technologies | Passionate About Design, Development, and Innovation </h2>
			</div>
			<div>
				<img src="" alt="Foto Nicolas Firpo">
			</div>
		</div>

		<ul class="flex gap-4 mt-4 ml-4 flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start">
			<li>
				<SocialPill href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicolasfirpo/"><LinkedinIcon class="size-4 md:size-6" />
				LinkedIn
				</SocialPill>
		
			</li>
			<li>
				<SocialPill href="https://github.com/niknef"><GithubIcon class="size-4 md:size-6" />Git Hub</a></SocialPill>
				
